  "Description": {
    "English": "A compact reactor unit, this engine is the heart of the Minotaur. It is mounted on a gyroscope to prevent fuel incidents during rapid movement.<br><br>Powered by conventional <span class=\"name name-fuel\">carbon-base fuels</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "该引擎是一个紧凑的反应堆单元，它是弥诺陶洛斯的核心。它被安装在陀螺仪上，以防止快速移动时发生燃油事故。<br><br>使用传统的<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳基燃料</span>驱动。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "精巧的反應器裝置，此引擎是彌諾陶洛斯的核心。安裝於陀螺儀上，以避免快速移動發生燃料意外。<br><br>動力來源為傳統<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳基燃料</span>。"
  },
